            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>The IAH relay ground circuit requires the use of vehicle circuit diagrams. See the applicable
                        truck Circuit Diagram Manual for circuit numbers and locations for fuses and connectors.
                    </para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
